<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>全球首款液氢重卡问世，搭载亿华通大功率发动机系统</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200910/e85a9c90723543bfaaee3cca4f28d599.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
